the movement of the record

00:11:37.060 --> 00:11:39.800
on the platter
allows us to do this.

00:11:39.800 --> 00:11:42.500
There's this other one here
called the waves-- hopefully

00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:46.540
I have the right
link here-- which

00:11:46.540 --> 00:11:52.600
adjusts the rotation in
a quick and slow fashion.

