00:12:22.810 --> 00:12:23.830
Questions?

00:12:23.830 --> 00:12:26.620
AUDIENCE: What's on the record?

00:12:26.620 --> 00:12:28.830
PROFESSOR: In that example?

00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:30.439
DJs like him and
