scratching over the word fresh.

00:50:52.640 --> 00:50:55.130
And these lines represent
changes in pitch

00:50:55.130 --> 00:50:56.330
that happen over time.

00:50:56.330 --> 00:51:00.010
So time is represented
on the x-axis.

00:51:00.010 --> 00:51:02.300
The y-axis is
showing the time it

00:51:02.300 --> 00:51:06.740
takes to move the sample
over that duration.

00:51:06.740 --> 00:51:09.091
Let's look at a little bit.

00:51:09.091 --> 00:51:12.570
[MUSIC - HERBIE HANCOCK,
 "ROCKIT"]

