rub come back again and again

00:53:10.150 --> 00:53:11.510
in different places.

00:53:11.510 --> 00:53:15.340
Finally, at the end, and
then in the closing phrase,

00:53:15.340 --> 00:53:17.230
we have some nice
variation where

00:53:17.230 --> 00:53:19.810
the expectations that have
been established so far,

00:53:19.810 --> 00:53:24.540
this opening motif,
is cut up and broken

00:53:24.540 --> 00:53:29.120
which creates a little
suspense, a little expectation

00:53:29.120 --> 00:53:31.690
