the turntable take

00:56:14.480 --> 00:56:17.130
on a special role in
the chorus of a song,

00:56:17.130 --> 00:56:19.190
whereas in a rock or
other popular context

00:56:19.190 --> 00:56:22.740
the chorus would be filled
by a big sing along.

00:56:22.740 --> 00:56:26.490
